            i1.getTxnId());
}

```

Unlike `groupingBy` (which takes a `Function` and then a `Collector`), `collectingAndThen` takes a collector (here, it&#39;s `toMap`) and then takes a `Function` (here, `Map::values`) that works on the result of the collector.

